Everything in sight: the tiny skirt of Kamensky did not cover the crotch
The star had to cross her legs tightly to avoid embarrassment
06 Nov 2019, 19:02 by Kristina CHERNIKOVA
read 107728 times
Nastya Kamensky, suffering from the Mexican heat, can, apparently, wear only clothes that cover only small areas of the body. In an interview for a radio in Mexico City, the beauty came to supermini. The skirt was more like a loincloth in size. Even the tucked-in shirt was longer and looked down.
Fans do not complain - they had a chance to enjoy the view of the naked legs of the artist. Men, as always, found Kamensky irresistible. There were also dissatisfied, who criticized the singer for a pose (the spelling and punctuation of the authors are preserved).
